Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.56,0:00:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.37,0:00:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the sky, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the jet limit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A heart-warming la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a million-horsepower engine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.64,0:00:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.66,0:00:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes wide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.31,0:00:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.78,0:00:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be off your guard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.96,0:00:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A righteous la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:00:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.31,0:01:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a seven-force power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If there could be only one resting place in this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.23,0:01:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that would be mother's lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.79,0:01:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,When Uran's not around,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I also crawl into mom's lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Ochanomizu, there's a package for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.72,0:01:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.80,0:01:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, here's your package.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.52,0:01:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but could you bring it inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This package is huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.68,0:01:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's quite big.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all mixed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a head!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.37,0:02:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mutilation murder case! Officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.53,0:02:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Black Looks
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? What? What an agitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! There seems to be a mutilation murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There are mutilated arms and legs. Look, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.09,0:02:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a robot...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's completely disassembled. I don't know what's what.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.41,0:02:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And the sender is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.31,0:02:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That part got wet, so I can't recognize letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But it smells like crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.54,0:02:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Two robots are mixed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's assemble this. We might find something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Since these are so small that it's hard to distinguish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.11,0:02:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it be fixed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakamura, can you turn the switch on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:02:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.79,0:03:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry! Turn the switch off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Is this the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.59,0:03:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.03,0:03:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.64,0:03:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like that head wasn't the right one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If it explodes again, it would be of great magnitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.75,0:03:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakamura, switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.80,0:03:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's fixed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Au.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Au.ro.ra.Looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.21,0:03:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Aurora Looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Hold on. No! Hold him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! I'll shoot if you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Aurora!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, Atom, it's me. Please come immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:04:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Aurora! Looks, Looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Aurora. Looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's that robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Aurora Looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.01,0:04:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Aurora Looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Aurora Looks
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks. Aurora Looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.92,0:04:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, it's speaking out of its faint old memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.09,0:04:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakamura. Maybe this robot is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.39,0:04:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Black Looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.03,0:04:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Black Looks? What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,0:04:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a gang group after robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.21,0:04:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The first place Black Looks appeared was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the car factory in West Germany, in April five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it, a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:05:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking just in case; the executive of this factory is a robot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Not only the executive, but all the workers here are robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. All robots. Then why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I beg you. I have a wife and kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.74,0:05:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What, a robot is begging for its life like a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Move expensive ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting with this case, they attacked
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,London's World Robot Bank,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Texas' Robot Oil Company, and South Africa's Robot Development Base
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and stole $80 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All crew members wear black masks
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,so no one know who they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Like you said, this robot
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,might be a victim of that Black Looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks. Looks. Aurora.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.74,0:06:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, so "Looks" comes from "Black Looks". Then what is "Aurora"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.93,0:06:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Aurora is an electric phenomenon in the stratosphere. Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned at school that there is a mountain called Aurora in the South Pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.64,0:06:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.11,0:06:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure this robot was sent from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If we take this robot to the South Pole, we might get a clue on Black Looks,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but it would be complicated to bring our police into the other country without any evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Robot is for a robot. How about I take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.09,0:06:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bit dangerous for Atom to investigate Black Looks by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor is... You are busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's the perfect one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.61,0:06:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He's aggressive and trustworthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined I would be able to travel in the South Pole with public money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, we are lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.48,0:06:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's hot. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.94,0:06:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-We are currently passing through the equator. -Equator?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on. Isn't there an air conditioner?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. You must be human, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.43,0:07:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid, I am. How can you bear such heat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, all the other passengers are robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When are we going to arrive at the South Pole?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,South Pole Penguin Land Airport
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.12,0:07:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We will go to downtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an announcement for passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a bus waiting at the front gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please have a safe ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, robots have to take that car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter, Atom. Get on this bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, even robots do pay for it. What's so wrong about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How come you are siding with this lump of metal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.63,0:07:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Lump of what? Say it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Siding with robots in Penguin Land? How funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.11,0:08:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'll just take that car. -Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This robot's got more sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking that one as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting. Are you going to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.11,0:08:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid, I'm the Mr. Beard who trained at the institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to police station first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a self-defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let me go! I'll walk on my own. -Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a self-defense. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, go to Aurora Mountain first. I'll catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:08:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That mountain is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-What wrong, Kid? -What's the name of that mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's Aurora Mountain. -As expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are going there, why don't you get in? I'm going to the same direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-You are a robot. -Ha ha, can you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You are nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't any hotel in Aurora Mountain. Would you like to come to my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, so many whales...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We built a ranch to protect and increase the number of whales
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that are becoming extinct every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Whale ranch. That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, that's my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an ice castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.78,0:09:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans must not be able to survive in this temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We should be thankful that we are robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems like the South Pole hates robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There weren't very many robots until a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:10:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why people are still treating robots like slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go! Call the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Until when are you going to keep me here without questioning?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use. Stop it. You will only exhaust yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate being in this kind of place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A day is nothing. I've been here for four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that more than 50 times now. Is that the only thing you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to hear about Black Looks?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll give you a dime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.65,0:10:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to get out of here until you die anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.18,0:10:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask me anything. I'll tell you anything I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I have tons of questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do Black Looks attack only robots?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a scary childhood memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He lost his mother to a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,To a robot? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.76,0:10:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have killed her quite terribly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he hates robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.74,0:10:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:11:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to work for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.42,0:11:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Who in the world is Black Looks?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not the time to be like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to escape. Will you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't waste your time. How are you going to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think of me so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's wrong? -Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-He fell. -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.38,0:11:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thief! Catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.73,0:12:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go into that field, you won't be able to come back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even need to chase him. Let him die out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.27,0:12:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's like this. Has anyone seen him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.81,0:12:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-Well... -I feel like I've seen him somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't work. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Jet is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.72,0:12:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Black mask! That's Black Looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.71,0:12:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-Black Looks? -He's going to kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to kill us all and steal all our money!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not someone whom we can fight back. Everyone, be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Let's fight together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.52,0:13:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No. We would never be able to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please wait for my signal in the top room of this house!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.94,0:13:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-What are you talking about? -We don't have time! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Let's hide first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes, sir! -Get rid of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.23,0:13:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you? Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiding won't save you. Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-Not here, either. -Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, it's now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.87,0:13:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, over there. On top of chandelier!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-They ran away! -Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Move back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Jet is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, let's steal a car and run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid, I will come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.57,0:14:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Robot hospital? Please come right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, we will wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.85,0:14:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,even though they are villains, they are human. No one can die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm out of gas here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather try my best than to freeze to death here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What a land of snowstorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.71,0:14:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's fallen down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be human to fall down because of a snowstorm. Help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! This one's that kid robot's company!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What? How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a fight with him at the airport this morning. Good. Let's shoot him and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.49,0:15:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on. I have a good idea. Burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.49,0:15:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can take revenge on that kid robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.03,0:15:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-Why is robot so kind? -I'm a nurse. It's a sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-Nurse robots are really good workers. -It's all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.99,0:15:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How can this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.59,0:15:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought her from Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent her to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This robot used to be a nurse working for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:15:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She had a kind heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:16:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She raised human orphans. Kids loved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, there was a huge upheaval for the advancement of robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She participated there and went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.91,0:16:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And a few days ago, as I was returning from house calls,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.71,0:16:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I found her terribly broken in scrap yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sad but here, robots are expendables.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't a place to fix such terribly broken robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.51,0:16:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I sent it to Doctor Ochanomizu in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, I found her head and other components.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.48,0:16:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to come to my office?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.61,0:16:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you awake, Mr. Beard?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.99,0:16:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Black Looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.87,0:16:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you surprised? This is my treasure storage. It's worth billions of dollars!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.90,0:16:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:17:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I'm a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.35,0:17:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't steal from humans. I'm only after robots!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an excuse! A thief is a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother was killed by a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Robot is my enemy. These are nothing compared to my mother's life...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.02,0:17:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you help me after getting paid,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,or will you get killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-All right. I'll take this much money. -Are you on my side now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting caught in electric wire? Poor you, Mr. Beard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.51,0:17:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Rosaline, who used to be our nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.02,0:17:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now all the riddles will be solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.21,0:17:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, this is Black Looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Beard? How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.07,0:18:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want him back, come to the valley of seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.87,0:18:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but it's about time to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.39,0:18:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you see some special execution event.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom will get here soon. As soon as he opens that door,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A 50,000-voltage electric current will flow to that pass and you will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Beard, please hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Beard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out, Black Looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here as I promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.49,0:18:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Beard is in that front room. Save him if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That door won't open that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, don't be fooled by him! As soon as the door opens, I will get toasted!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, no! Please don't come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Something was suspicious, so I entered without opening the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.77,0:19:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.69,0:19:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, catch Black Looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes! -Don't miss him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.23,0:19:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, it's my defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then take that mask off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.69,0:20:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so shocking about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.59,0:20:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You are only about a middle school student...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.54,0:20:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Revenge is a scary thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, do whatever pleases you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.89,0:20:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks, can you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You might not remember since you were too young, but I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rosaline!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.87,0:20:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.92,0:21:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No, my mom's dead. You are fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.56,0:21:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks, have you forgotten my voice? I didn't forget you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I got broken, you became alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.71,0:21:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.05,0:21:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom was human. She died.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How can a human be born out of a robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.19,0:21:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You were an orphan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.89,0:21:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I hid my identity and raised you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In this country, it's unforgivable for a robot to raise a human baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.52,0:21:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I participated in that protest for the advancement of robots
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,because I wanted to be acknowledged as your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.13,0:21:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But I got destroyed by someone who was against that protest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.38,0:21:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks, do you understand? Call her mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.77,0:22:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.28,0:22:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's mom's lap you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.75,0:22:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.20,0:22:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.07,0:22:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If there could be only one resting place...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.30,0:22:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A huge scrap that fell from the night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.18,0:22:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,After assembling them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.61,0:22:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It became a very powerful-looking robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.93,0:22:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.26,0:22:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Garon?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.30,0:22:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Garon who remodels everything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.30,0:22:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,started spreading poisonous gas in a deserted island in the South.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.60,0:22:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No latest jet or missile won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.25,0:22:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Garon! I'm for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.02,0:22:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy, "The Devil Garon". Look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.39,0:22:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy, "The Devil Garon"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.32,0:23:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My arms and legs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.33,0:23:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,fly over the sky with a jet
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.85,0:23:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.97,0:23:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.72,0:23:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside my waist,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.67,0:23:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,a machine gun's light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.20,0:23:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.31,0:23:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.47,0:23:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Searchlight's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.15,0:23:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser Blast's hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.72,0:23:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven powers, Wa Wa Wa Wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.94,0:23:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We fight for the peace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:24:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go together
